recruiting and

19:13.085 --> 19:15.988 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
holding on to good teachers is
an uphill battle.

19:16.022 --> 19:18.858 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
The district also faces a common
