19:27.500 --> 19:30.469 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Lisa Stark of Education Week has
the story.

19:30.503 --> 19:38.644 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
LISA STARK: It's summer in the
city of Chicago,
the nation's third largest
public school district.

19:38.677 --> 19:45.718 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And these aspiring teachers are
getting to
know each other, the first step
in an intensive

19:45.751 --> 19:50.022 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
