from backgrounds like myself get
these opportunities.

19:59.298 --> 20:05.171 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
LISA STARK: These fellows, 21 of
them, are
all students at Illinois State
University,

20:05.204 --> 20:07.006 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
training to be teachers.

20:07.039 --> 20:12.378 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
They have high hopes, but most,
like Morgan
Brauer, have little or no
experience in the

20:12.411 --> 20:14.780 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
inner city.

20:14.814 --> 20:19.318 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
We first met Morgan the day
before, at her
home about an hour away.

20:19.351 --> 20:21.320 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Tell me about this neighborhood,
how you grew
up?

20:21.353 --> 20:24.924 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MORGAN BRAUER, Student, Illinois
State University:
So, I'm from the suburbs of
Chicago, Rolling

20:24.957 --> 20:26.659 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
Meadows specifically.

20:26.692 --> 20:32.465 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
LISA STARK: Morgan typifies
