force, mostly white, mostly
female.

20:32.498 --> 20:37.169 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MORGAN BRAUER: I grew up, it's
everyone basically
goes to college.

20:37.203 --> 20:39.939 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
