31:32.157 --> 31:38.096 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: With all of
this, even with
the lopsided 3-1
advantage-disadvantage, Trump

31:38.130 --> 31:42.501 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
