you have to
apply for a license.

39:43.348 --> 39:50.388 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And this means that actually
normal people
are able actually to take part
in this boom,

39:50.421 --> 39:51.556 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
this tourism boom.

39:51.589 --> 39:54.425 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
HALLDOR MAR: This country is not
for Icelanders
anymore.

39:54.459 --> 39:57.395 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
It's more for tourists.

39:57.428 --> 40:01.099 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I'm looking at maybe we just
have to move
abroad.

40:01.132 --> 40:06.037 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
